{"tid":1349910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議任何 親中共的人，統一叫共匪","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T11:32:26.000Z","uid":7736,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef690874d987a38cb669f7fa77e9a09b003e91e5","tid":1349910,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"建議任何 親中共的人，統一叫共匪（不論幫中共政府的人，為中共講野的大陸人，收穩穩費的，亂9打人的黑幫等等，損害香港同香港人，人權與利益的人都叫共匪）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標籤化 都係反擊的一種，<br />\n想有用依個名詞話比佢地聽，佢地幾樣衰！<br />\n政府口口聲聲，講我地係暴徒，妖魔化香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n共匪 足唔足夠表達到？<br />\n有冇其他更好的叫法？"},{"pid":"a4786e63cf9fa2c69aa0692b93ed78a25a8b4b4d","tid":1349910,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:30:15.000Z","msg":"何君堯中環皇后大道中5號衡怡大廈18樓律師樓好太平<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1349881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1349881</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1dd0cbb6b90a24bdd4effdd1a0a3341d38ad11b6","tid":1349910,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hi-on.org.tw/Public/Image/1-12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hi-on.org.tw%2FPublic%2FImage%2F1-12.jpg&h=7310b022&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}